metadata.name: Landscapes #1
metadata.description:
EDITION OF 10

Title: Landscapes  
Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2021  
Minted: 2022

Landscapes by Godwits is a collection of 100 multi-edition works that give tribute to Refik Anadol's Synthetic Dreams Landscapes. The works in this collection present abstract works created using Generative Adversarial Network, 3D Design, Graphic Design Software & Analog Mediums. Godwits is a RAS Community Leader who wanted to give back to the community & airdropped the collection to over 500 collectors.

**The works in this collection are not affiliated with Refik Anadol or RAS.

Published By: Abstract Art Labs LLC
